OL,3,CSummer camp leader, 76, admits
OL,4,Cdrugging children with sedative-laced
OL,5,Csweets
OL,7,FA 76-year-old man has admitted
OL,8,Fdrugging and sexually assaulting
OL,9,Fseveral boys at a children's summer
OL,10,Fcamp.
OL,12,FJohn Ruben laced sweets with
OL,13,Ftranquillising drugs and attacked two
OL,14,Fchildren after asking youngsters to
OL,15,Fplay "a sweet game", Leicester Crown
OL,16,FCourt heard.
OL,18,FIt comes after a number of children
OL,19,Ffell ill at Stathern Lodge on Canal
OL,20,FLane in Stathern, near Melton Mowbray
OL,21,Fin Leicestershire on Sunday 27 July.
