OL,7,FEmergency services attended the scene
OL,8,Fthe day after receiving the report.
OL,10,FEight children, all boys aged between
OL,11,Feight and 11, were taken to hospital
OL,12,Fas a precaution, said police.
OL,14,FAn adult was also taken to the
OL,15,Fhospital as a precaution, with all
OL,16,Fnine people later discharged.
OL,18,FProsecutor Mary Prior KC told the
OL,19,Fcourt: "The defendant, for at least 27
OL,20,Fyears, has run a holiday camp.
