OL,7,F"The game is that each has to eat
OL,8,Freally sticky sweets as quickly as
OL,9,Fthey can but they must chew them.
OL,11,F"Children have always felt ill the
OL,12,Fnext day but he explained it as they
OL,13,Fwere overwrought."
OL,15,FEarlier this year, Ruben's stepson
OL,16,Fcalled the police when he became
OL,17,Fsuspicious.
