OL,7,FWhen police arrived, they found items
OL,8,Fthat belonged to Ruben including baby
OL,9,Foil, syringes with white powder inside
OL,10,Fand sweets laced with drugs.
OL,12,FRuben, of Wayte Court, Ruddington,
OL,13,FNottinghamshire, admitted sexual
OL,14,Fassault of a child under 13, assault
OL,15,Fof a child under 13 by penetration,
OL,16,Feight counts of child cruelty, three
OL,17,Fcounts of making indecent images of
OL,18,Fchildren and four drugs charges.
